			<xsd:documentation source="http://www.openapplications.org/oagis/10">When the receiver of this Credit provides the credit management function.  If the sender is the accounts receivable application, the OpenItemAmount is the only required amount field.  When the sender is the customer order management application, the OrderAmount is the only required amount field. 

